Invocation Name: speedy snacks
des:
Your very own personal chef at your fingertips, armed with a plethora of recipe inspiration anytime you may need it!

Ingredients are listed from the outset so you can be sure you have everything required before you embark on a delicious creation. 

To start simply ask Alexa to 'Open Speedy Snacks' and request something such as 'can I have a lunch recipe', then let Chef Alex do the rest!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
